title: Rockk Looking for members.
body:
A multi game discord group with heavy league focus,

Don't need to be good, Every level of play is good enough, from wood 11 to faker -1

And there are plenty of other things to do as well, from an ongoing anything rp to grabbing your new friends for other games, It's all good on Rockk.

Link to a welcome page is here.
https://discordapp.com/invite/4rKQYYk
